➜恒驰首期六款车全球发布！款款惊艳
http://www.sohu.com/a/411253664_255783	36442
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=207979897&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新能源汽车领域一家独大的格局即将改变。8月3日，恒驰首期六款车在上海、广州同时亮相，恒驰1、恒驰2、恒驰3、恒驰4、恒驰5、恒驰6正式揭开面纱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200803/651b978dddd143b886831366bdcc5f2b.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">许家印宣布恒驰首期6款车同时发布</span></img></p>
